0:13:37.088,000 --> 0:13:39,000
and in so many of her friends

255
0:13:39.334,000 --> 0:13:41,000
and her peers.

256
0:13:43.019,000 --> 0:13:44,000
As Kyla said,

257
0:13:44.77,000 --> 0:13:47,000
"Ms. Val, I literally felt myself walk taller as the season went on,

